# Casino API Endpoints

## Authentication
POST   /api/Auth/register                Register a new user account.
POST   /api/Auth/login                   Authenticate and receive a JWT token.

## Users
GET    /api/Users                        Retrieve all users.
GET    /api/Users/{id}                   Retrieve a user by ID.
PUT    /api/Users/{id}                   Update user details.
DELETE /api/Users/{id}                   Remove a user.

## Financial Transactions
GET    /api/FinancialTransactions        List all financial transactions.
GET    /api/FinancialTransactions/user/{userId}  List transactions for a user.
POST   /api/FinancialTransactions        Create a financial transaction.

## Games
GET    /api/Games                        List all games.
GET    /api/Games/{id}                   Get game details by ID.
POST   /api/Games                        Add a new game.
PUT    /api/Games/{id}                   Update a game.
DELETE /api/Games/{id}                   Delete a game.

## Games With Ratio
GET    /api/GamesWithRatio               List all games with payout ratios.
GET    /api/GamesWithRatio/{id}          Get game with ratio by ID.

## Game Transactions
GET    /api/GameTransactions             List all game transactions.
GET    /api/GameTransactions/user/{userId}  List game transactions for a user.
POST   /api/GameTransactions             Create a game transaction.

## User History
GET    /api/UserHistory/user/{userId}    Get game history for a user.

## Roulette
POST   /api/Roulette/spin                Place a bet and spin the roulette.

## Slots
POST   /api/Slots/spin                   Simulate a slot spin with a bet.